snippet.title: Super Luigi Wii: The Emissary (NSMBFMD Release Trailer)
snippet.description:
SLWii: The Emissary is a a complete revamp of Ultimate Super Luigi Wii that was released in a rush and unpolished state back in 2020.

Based around Newer SMBWii, The Emissary stars Luigi in an adventure heavily inspired from Super Smash Bros Melee and Brawl with custom music, models and inspirations coming from those respective games.

​Oh and did I mention we have a custom never before seen power-up?

Features:
- 15 Revamped Levels
- Custom World Map(s)
- Birth of a New Power-Up!
- Custom SFX
- Custom Final Boss
- The Great Maze (with checkpoints)
- Hidden Luigi's in every level, can you find them all?

Current version: V1.0.2a
Download: https://iggy3434.weebly.com

You can also catch the entire NSMBFMD here where this mod and many others are featured: https://youtu.be/40OUE8quoz4

Also please stop asking me for a wbfs. DOLPHIN HAS RIIVOLUTION SUPPORT.
